  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As an <strong>action</strong>, you gain the ability to see through solid objects to a range of 30 feet. Within that range, you have @Item[rkSDNVeg7HvhhPKe]{Darkvision}&nbsp;if you don&rsquo;t already have it.</p>\n<p>This special sight lasts for 1 minute or until your concentration ends (as if you were concentrating on a spell). During that time, you perceive objects as ghostly, transparent images.</p>\n<p>Once you use this invocation, you can&rsquo;t use it again until you finish a short or long rest.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">FoundryVTT</strong><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">: This is not automated</span></p>",
